About this hotel

This informal hotel is 3 km from Majorelle Garden, 4 km from the buzzing Jemaa el-Fnaa square and 5 km from Bahia Palace.

Check-out time: 12:00 PM

    Hivernage

    Refined, modern Hivernage is known for nightlife, with a casino, cocktail lounges, hotel dance clubs and chic global restaurants with live music. The Royal Theatre, with domes and Ancient Egyptian–style columns, stages concerts in an amphitheater. Nearby, the Menara Gardens, with a huge reflecting pool and mountains in the background, date to the 12th century, and El-Harti Park has fountains and a rose garden.

    About this hotel

    This informal hotel is 3 km from Majorelle Garden, 4 km from the buzzing Jemaa el-Fnaa square and 5 km from Bahia Palace. …

    Unassuming rooms with tile floors offer free Wi-Fi, cable TV and en suite bathrooms, as well as air-conditioning. Suites add separate living areas.

    Breakfast and parking are complimentary. Other amenities include 2 restaurants, a salon and a tea lounge, plus a spa with a hammam and a sauna. There's also meeting space, a gym and an outdoor pool.
